#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Please note that some of these settings may depend on your selected icon "
#| "theme. &kde; comes with three icon themes by default, Oxygen, Monochrome "
#| "and Crystal SVG. There are additional color themes in the kdeartwork "
